channel.title: Adding custom items, PLEASE HELP!
channel.description:
Okay, so i made a little private server with crazyface's client.
I downloaded some custom items from the models topic. I took the ints en placed them in the class8.java and i put the .gz stuff in the models folder. I go into my server and type: add model 14009 and add model 14008 and it says the models are perfectly added. But when i type the good ::pickup id it gaves me a dwarf remain seed thingy!
Can someone please help me? Or give me a good tut with adding custom items, because i dont understand a damn shit of this: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php?topic=262499.0
